<item>
            <title>[LU-14004] memory leak in ll_update_default_lsm_md()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14004</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When multiple processes call ll_update_default_lsm_md() at the same time, it should check whether lli_default_lsm_md is set, if so, free it before setting it to the one from lustre_md, otherwise it will be set to the last one, and the default_lsm set before it are leaked. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
